A%20%20%20%20%20%20I've%20got%20this%20recurring%20shark%20dream.%20%20Sounds%20scary%2C%20huh%3F%0A%20%20%0AExcept%2C%20it's%20just%20me%20running%20through%20a%20dry%20sewer%20and%20the%20shark%20trying%20desperately%20to%20catch%20up.%20%20As%20there's%20no%20water%2C%20the%20shark%20is%20forced%20to%20flop%20around%20and%20pull%20itself%20along%20with%20its%20fins%20...%20but%2C%20you%20know%2C%20menancingly.%20%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%0A%20%20%20%20%0A%3C%2Fpost%3E%0A%0A%3Cdate%3E02%2CAugust%2C2004%3C%2Fdate%3E%0A%3Cpost%3E%0A%0A%09%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20William%20Gibson%20%20urlLink%20waxes%20%20nostalgic%20on%20outmoded%20tech%2C%20including%20a%20grade%20school%20favorite%2C%20the%20mimeograph%3A%20%22You%20typed%2C%20once%2C%20on%20a%20waxed%20paper%20'stencil'%2C%20clipped%20this%20over%20a%20silkscreen%20device%20with%20a%20moving%20pad%20or%20drum%20of%20ink%20behind%20it%2C%20and%20your%20mimeograph%20ran%20off%20(or%20silkscreened%2C%20really)%20as%20many%20copies%20of%20your%20document%20as%20you%20required.%20Owing%20to%20the%20physical%20peculiarities%20of%20the%20medium%2C%20though%2C%20it%20was%20unwise%20to%20underline%20too%20frequently%20on%20a%20mimeograph%20stencil%3A%20the%20single%20unbroken%20line%20was%20particularly%20prone%20to%20tear%2C%20producing%20leaks%20and%20smudging.%22%20%0A%20urlLink%20Jason%20%2C%20Aaron%20and%20I%20were%20talking%20about%20the%20mimeograph%20and%20other%20printing%20processes%20and%20we%20couldn't%20figure%20out%20why%20blueprints%20were%20still%20in%20use%20since%20they%20seemed%20to%20involve%20such%20a%20wacky%20production%20process.%20%20I%20imagine%20it's%20both%20because%20of%20size%20and%20because%20draftsmen%20draw%20on%20trace.%0A%20%20%0AI%20didn't%20remember%20the%20details%20at%20the%20time%2C%20but%20blueprinting%20is%20a%20wild%20scene.%20%20It%20was%20invented%20by%20%20urlLink%20John%20Herschel%20%20in%201840%20(his%20father%20discovered%20that%20funny%20planet%20between%20Saturn%20and%20Neptune).%20%20It%20involves%20%20urlLink%20coating%20%20a%20piece%20of%20paper%20with%20a%20chemical%20whose%20structure%20is%20unknown%20and%20then%20explosing%20it%20to%20a%20ridiculously%20strong%20light.%20%20The%20process%20is%20so%20old%20that%20the%20blue%20produced%20is%20referred%20to%20as%20Prussian%20blue.%20%20That's%20like%20having%20a%20color%20called%20Ottoman%20orange.%0A%20%20%0AI%20know%20it's%20still%20somewhat%20used%20because%20I%20saw%20the%20blueprint%20machine%20that%20belongs%20to%20the%20city%20of%20Baltimore%20do%20its%20crazy%20photochemical%20voodoo.%20%20Leave%20it%20to%20Charm%20City%20to%20keep%20alchemy%20alive.%0A%20%20%20%20%20%0A%20%20%20%20%0A%3C%2Fpost%3E%0A%0A%3Cdate%3E02%2CAugust%2C2004%3C%2Fdate%3E%0A%3Cpost%3E%0A%0A%09%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20My%20stepdad%20is%20a%20vet%20with%20a%20purple%20heart%20and%20I'm%20a%20whiny%20liberal%20who%20lives%20in%20San%20Francisco%20...%20which%20is%20why%20I'm%20often%20confused%20that%20we%20both%20love%20Full%20Metal%20Jacket.%20%20I%20think%20it%20comes%20down%20to%20appreciating%20the%20movie%20as%20a%20true%20depiction%20of%20what%20it%20was%20like%20to%20go%20to%20Vietnam%20vs.%20a%20statement%20of%20why%20not%20to%20go%20to%20Vietnam%20in%20the%20first%20place.%0A%20%20%0A%20urlLink%20Kottke%20%20recently%20said%20something%20related%20to%20this%2C%20%22it%20must%20be%20difficult%20to%20recruit%20someone%20who%20has%20seen%20the%20first%2015%20minutes%20of%20Saving%20Private%20Ryan%20or%20Full%20Metal%20Jacket%20(although%20some%20may%20sign%20up%20because%20of%20such%20films).%22%0A%20%20%0AIt%20turns%20out%20the%20parenthetical%20is%20the%20truer%20part%20-%20at%20least%2C%20according%20to%20%20urlLink%20Anthony%20Swofford%20's%20Desert%20Storm%20memoir%2C%20Jarhead.%20%20In%20it%20he%20%20urlLink%20says%20%2C%20%22Vietnam%20War%20films%20are%20all%20pro-war%2C%20no%20matter%20what%20the%20supposed%20message%2C%20what%20Kubrick%20or%20Coppola%20or%20Stone%20intended.%20.%20.%20The%20magic%20brutality%20of%20the%20films%20celebrates%20the%20terrible%20and%20despicable%20beauty%20of%20their%20fighting%20skills.%20Fight%2C%20rape%2C%20war%2C%20pillage%2C%20burn.%20Filmic%20images%20of%20death%20and%20carnage%20are%20pornography%20for%20the%20military%20man.''%0A%20%20%0AObviously%20there's%20a%20great%20documentary%20to%20be%20made%20on%20the%20free%20play%20of%20signs%20and%20signifiers%20involved%20when%20soldiers%20watch%20anti-war%20war%20movies%20in%20the%20battlefield.%20%20But%20moreover%20it%20shows%20that%20depictions%20of%20war%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20political%20intent%2C%20are%20compelling%20because%20of%20the%20horror%2C%20not%20in%20spite%20of%20it.%0A%20%20%20%20%20%0A%20%20%20%20%0A%3C%2Fpost%3E%0A%0A%3Cdate%3E02%2CAugust%2C2004%3C%2Fdate%3E%0A%3Cpost%3E%0A%0A%09%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20Last%20Thursday%2C%20I%20saw%20where%20the%20internet%20%20urlLink%20lives%20.%20%20It%20lives%20in%20a%20cold%2C%20glass%20%20urlLink%20box%20%20protected%20by%20biometric%20scanners%20and%20a%20regulated%20power%20supply%20the%20size%20of%20a%20bus.%20%20Knowing%20I%20had%20no%20business%20in%20the%20holy%20of%20holies%2C%20the%20internet%20winked%20at%20me%20as%20I%20trundled%20off%20to%20the%20Blogger%20alcove.%0A%20%20%0AI'd%20never%20thought%20of%20internet%20security%20in%20terms%20of%20floor-to-ceiling%20black%20metal%20cages%2C%20but%20that's%20how%20it%20works%20where%20the%20electronic%20meets%20the%20physical.%20%20I%20never%20thought%20the%20internet%20had%20an%20off%20switch%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20start%20to%20see%20a%20set%20of%20emergency%20shutdown%20switches%20that%20would%20bring%20down%20the%20entire%20data%20center.%20%20Of%20course%2C%20like%20launching%20nuclear%20weapons%2C%20you%20have%20to%20press%20both%20buttons%20at%20the%20same%20time.%0A%20%20%0AI%20once%20knew%20a%20responsible%2C%20well-mannered%20young%20woman%20who%2C%20as%20a%20girl%2C%20set%20off%20the%20fire%20alarm%20in%20her%20elementary%20school.%20%20Not%20out%20of%20mischief%20aforethought%2C%20but%20just%20because%20she%20felt%20her%20hand%20drawn%20to%20the%20big%2C%20red%20switch.%20%20The%20alarm%20pulled%20her.%0A%20%20%0ABest%20not%20to%20think%20of%20such%20things.%0A%20%20%20%20%20%0A%20%20%20%20%0A%3C%2Fpost%3E%0A%0A%3Cdate%3E02%2CAugust%2C2004%3C%2Fdate%3E%0A%3Cpost%3E%0A%0A%09%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20last%20night's%20Caltrain%20conductor%20when%20he%20said%2C%20%22We're%20now%20arriving%20in%20downtown%20SF%20...%20or%20at%20least%20as%20close%20as%20we%20get%20to%20it.%22%0A%20%20%0AThe%20other%20passengers%20came%20around%20when%20he%20added%2C%20%22Please%20remember%20to%20gather%20all%20your%20personal%20belonings%20before%20leaving.%20%20Any%20items%20left%20behind%20will%20be%20seized%20and%20ground%20into%20a%20fine%20powder.%20%20The%20powder%20will%20then%20be%20turned%20into%20a%20launchpad%20which%20Caltrain%20will%20use%20to%20go%20to%20the%20moon.%22%0A%20%20%20%20%20%0A%20%20%20%20%0A%3C%2Fpost%3E%0A%0A%3Cdate%3E02%2CAugust%2C2004%3C%2Fdate%3E%0A%3Cpost%3E%0A%0A%09%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20Last%20night%2C%20someone%20asked%20%20urlLink%20Ev%20%20if%20he%20was%20related%20to%20a%20clan%20of%20Williamses%20from%20Out%20East.%20%20Oh%2C%20the%20pain%20of%20over-common%20last%20names.%20%20It%20made%20me%20recall%20the%20time%20I%20was%20offered%20condolences%20for%20the%20relative%20of%20mine%20that%20OJ%20killed.%0A%20%20%0AHappily%2C%20I%20also%20remembered%20my%20out-east%20friend%20John%20Williams%20who%20isn't%20the%20famous%20composer%20but%20once%20convinced%20someone%20to%20the%20contrary.%0A%20%0A%20You're%20John%20Williams%20...%20the%20composer%3F!%20%20%20%0ASure.%20%20%0A%20But%20you're%20so%20young!%20%20You%20must%20have%20been%20a%20little%20kid%20when%20Jaws%20came%20out.%20%20%20%0AWell%2C%20yeah%2C%20but%20my%20early%20work%20wasn't%20really%20that%20complex.%20%20I%20mean%2C%20how%20hard%20is%20'DUH-nuh%20...%20DUH-nuh.'%0A%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%0A%