the%20renowned%20Brazilian%20fishlet%20known%20as%20%20candiru%20%2C%20which%20likes%20to%20swim%20up%20a%20man's%20urine%20stream%20and%20lodge%20in%20the%20urethra%20with%20a%20ring%20of%20retrorse%20spines%20preventing%20its%20removal%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20very%20rare%20circumstances%20in%20which%20doctor%20(sic)%20will%20perform%20the%20operation%2C%20known%20as%20peotomy.%20%0ANote%20to%20self%3A%20never%20pee%20in%20Brazil.%0A%20%20%20%20%20%0A%20%20%20%20%0A%3C%2Fpost%3E%0A%0A%3Cdate%3E02%2CAugust%2C2004%3C%2Fdate%3E%0A%3Cpost%3E%0A%0A%09%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20%20urlLink%20%20%20My%20family%20came%20out%20to%20visit%20me%20in%20San%20Francisco%20during%20Christmas.%20%20It's%20like%20going%20home%20for%20the%20holidays%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20have%20to%20go%20anywhere.%0A%20%20%0AThe%20non-trip%20was%20a%20blast%2C%20and%20I%20had%20an%20especially%20great%20time%20hanging%20out%20with%20my%20brother.%20%20Because%20we%20don't%20see%20each%20other%20for%20long%20stretches%20at%20a%20time%2C%20there's%20a%20lot%20I%20forget%20-%20specifically%20how%20much%20fun%20it%20is%20to%20have%20a%20brother.%20%20First%20off%2C%20little%20brothers%20are%20just%20so%20butterflying%20game%20for%20anything.%20%20Do%20you%20know%20how%20I%20got%20David%20to%20pose%20for%20this%20photo%3F%20%20I%20said%2C%20%22Look%2C%20there's%20some%20big%20old%20nasty%20seaweed%20...%20pick%20it%20up%20and%20pretend%20to%20eat%20it%20-%20I%20want%20to%20post%20pictures%20of%20that%20on%20the%20Internet.%22%20%20Awesome.%0A%20%20%0AAlso%2C%20whenever%20we%20hang%20out%20it's%20like%20a%20giant%20dork%20braindump.%20%20%22Here's%20every%20game%2C%20scifi%20show%20and%20geeky%20thing%20I've%20seen%20since%20last%20we%20met.%22%20%20My%20friends%20pointed%20out%20how%20similar%20we%20are%20in%20appearance%20and%2C%20like%2C%20vocal%20mannerisms.%20%20Obviously%2C%20this%20is%20to%20be%20expected.%20%20As%20Sutter%20said%2C%20%22Is%20he%20not%20the%20person%20you've%20shared%20a%20bedroom%20with%20the%20longest%3F%22%20%20%0A%20%20%0AIt%20kicks%20ass.%20%20There's%20like%20this%20other%20me%20living%20in%20Providence%20but%20with%20special%20skills.%20%20Example%3A%20%20%0AMe%3A%20Hey%2C%20Eugene.%20%20Did%20you%20know%20my%20brother%20can%20sing%20the%20music%20from%20any%20video%20game%20he%20has%20ever%20played%3F%20%0AEugene%3A%20Okay%2C%20how%20'bout%20Rygar%3F%20%0ADavid%3A%20The%20first%20screen%20or%20the%20opening%20level%3F%20%0A%20%0AGood%20work%2C%20Mom.%20%20You%20done%20raised%20us%20right.%0A%20%20%20%20%20%0A%20%20%20%20%0A%3C%2Fpost%3E%0A%0A%3Cdate%3E02%2CAugust%2C2004%3C%2Fdate%3E%0A%3Cpost%3E%0A%0A%09%20%0A%20%20%20%20%20%20In%20the%20commentary%20for%20Fear%20and%20Loathing%20in%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20you%20get%20some%20of%20the%20dirt%20as%20to%20why%20the%20original%20director%2C%20Alex%20Cox%2C%20was%20dumped%20from%20the%20project.%20%20The%20producer%2C%20Laila%20Nabulsi%20talks%20about%20how%20there%20were%20creative%20differences%20and%20that%20it%20had%20something%20to%20do%20with%20the%20inclusion%20of%20the%20Wave%20Speech%20from%20the%20book.%20%20That's%20the%20one%20that%20goes%3A%20%0AWe%20had%20all%20the%20momentum%3B%20we%20were%20riding%20the%20crest%20of%20a%20high%20and%20beautiful%20wave.%20So%20now%2C%20less%20than%20five%20years%20later%2C%20you%20can%20go%20up%20on%20a%20steep%20hill%20in%20Las%20Vegas%20and%20look%20West%2C%20and%20with%20the%20right%20kind%20of%20eyes%20you%20can%20almost%20see%20the%20high-water%20mark---the%20place%20where%20the%20wave%20finally%20broke%20and%20rolled%20back.%20%0AIn%20the%20new%20documentary%2C%20%20urlLink%20Breakfast%20with%20Hunter%20%2C%20you%20get%20a%20much%20more%20detailed%20picture%20of%20what%20went%20down.%20%20Filmmaker%20Wayne%20Ewing%20is%20there%20at%20Owl%20Farm%20when%20Alex%20Cox%20and%20co-writer%20Tod%20Davies%20come%20to%20visit%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20script%20...%20which%20Hunter's%20not%20read.%20%20So%20he's%20caught%20flat-footed%20when%20he%2